{"TopicId":182828,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"The New End-User License Agreement is Unacceptable","CreatedByName":"T.C.","CreatedById":111697,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-09-24T02:20:38Z","PageNum":6,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Chel","CreatedById":176173,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T06:59:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558123\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552460253\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIgnorance is indeed bliss.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, they\u2019ve added a clause that basically guarantee they emerge victorious in any legal dispute.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy lord, is that legal?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T07:03:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558125\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552460354\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Cat_In_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, The_Cat_In_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy lord, is that legal?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour silence makes it legal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u2019re talking commercial disputes, of course, where at your own signature (the one that you made by accepting the EULA all that time ago) you may consent to the case being arbitrated under North Korean law, and everything in between.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chel","CreatedById":176173,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T07:04:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh, I see. I\u0027m not planning to get into any legal disputes with T2 so I\u0027ll just pay it no attention and carry on (after all, I\u0027m here for the game)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T08:56:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558128\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552460662\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022176173\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The_Cat_In_Space\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, The_Cat_In_Space said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E not planning to \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eget into any legal\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E disputes...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... The same way that everyone plans not to get mugged.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s probability, not plans.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T11:57:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552467376\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298447\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YNM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... The same way that everyone plans not to get mugged.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s probability, not plans.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMugging happen every day though. Private individuals running afoul of a EULA is an extremely rare event. And even then I personally\u00A0have never heard of it happening outside of instances of large scale piracy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe Im wrong but IMO, people get way too overexcited about EULA matters.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T12:00:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558193\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552478233\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPrivate\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E individuals running afoul of a EULA is an extremely rare event\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E.\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDepends on the EULA. You might want to double check what is inside of it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T12:27:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2 All, first of all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you not forget making your KSP releases backup?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkFighter","CreatedById":168628,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T13:34:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe arbitration\u00A0clause is not binding in Germany, both parties have to\u003Cem\u003E\u00A0sign\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0a \u003Cem\u003Eseparate\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0document in this case.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T15:00:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558193\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552478233\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMugging happen every day though. Private individuals running afoul of a EULA is an extremely rare event. And even then I personally\u00A0have never heard of it happening outside of instances of large scale piracy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe Im wrong but IMO, people get way too overexcited about EULA matters.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was one odd EULA on Steam that allowed the representatives of the publisher to inspect the location the game is being played in, and the device it\u2019s being played on, at any moment in time without prior warning.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T15:13:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558283\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552489243\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was one odd EULA on Steam that allowed the representatives of the publisher to inspect the location the game is being played in, and the device it\u2019s being played on, at any moment in time without prior warning.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHonestly - Im trying hard to be concerned but its not coming.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-03-13T15:14:05Z\u0022 title=\u002203/13/2019 03:14  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 13, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by p1t1o\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T15:39:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust keep in mind that no EULA is above the local law, so most cases of these unconventional\u00A0EULA texts\u00A0are not enforceable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T15:50:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd make backup copies of the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T16:36:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558302\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552491574\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002245577\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Shpaget\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n54 minutes ago, Shpaget said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust keep in mind that no EULA is above the local law, so most cases of these unconventional\u00A0EULA texts\u00A0are not enforceable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn top of that, at\u00A0least once I have heard of a judge throwing out a EULA case based solely on the length of the agreement and how nobody could be expected to fully read \u0026amp; digest it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kernel Kraken","CreatedById":181383,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-13T21:57:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022156614\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552467376\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298447\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YNM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 hours ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... The same way that everyone plans not to get mugged.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s probability, not plans.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMolotov cocktails thrown through a large corporation\u0027s window are an effective way of getting around forced arbitration. Same thing with a mugging.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease don\u0027t take this seriously.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI only condone revolution if the benefits outweigh the costs and risk of jail time is less than 60 percent. Like getting rid of the Brits, or getting rid of a cash grab EULA.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-03-13T21:59:55Z\u0022 title=\u002203/13/2019 09:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 13, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Kernel Kraken\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-03-14T00:25:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223558615\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022182828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221552514254\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181383\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kernel Kraken\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Kernel Kraken said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI only\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E condone revolution\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E if the benefits outweigh the costs and risk of jail time is less than 60 \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Epercent\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d always argue \u0022cock-up before conspiracy\u0022, but sometimes, conspiracy exists...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}